   "source": [
    "# 1.4 接口（interface）\n",
    "\n",
    "> 目标：理解 `interface` 的用法，以及与 `type` 的区别"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 什么是接口？\n",
    "\n",
    "`interface` 用于定义对象的结构，和 `type` 类似但有扩展能力。\n",
    "\n",
    "```typescript\n",
    "interface GatewayConfig {\n",
    "  port: number;\n",
    "  host: string;\n",
    "  verbose?: boolean;  // ? 表示可选\n",
    "}\n",
    "\n",
    "// 使用接口\n",
    "const config: GatewayConfig = {\n",
    "  port: 8080,\n",
    "  host: \"localhost\",\n",
    "  verbose: true\n",
    "};\n",
    "```"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "// 定义接口\n",
    "interface GatewayConfig {\n",
    "  port: number;\n",
    "  host: string;\n",
    "  verbose?: boolean;\n",
    "}\n",
    "\n",
    "// 实现接口\n",
    "const config: GatewayConfig = {\n",
    "  port: 8080,\n",
    "  host: \"localhost\",\n",
    "  verbose: true\n",
    "};\n",
    "\n",
    "// 函数使用接口作为参数类型\n",
    "function startGateway(cfg: GatewayConfig): string {\n",
    "  return `启动网关: ${cfg.host}:${cfg.port}`;\n",
    "}\n",
    "\n",
    "console.log(startGateway(config));\n",
    "\n",
    "undefined;"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## type vs interface：什么时候用哪个？\n",
    "\n",
    "| 特性 | `type` | `interface` |\n",
    "|------|--------|-------------|\n",
    "| 定义对象结构 | ✅ | ✅ |\n",
    "| 联合类型 | ✅ `type A = B \| C` | ❌ |\n",
    "| 扩展 | ❌ | ✅ `extends` |\n",
    "| 重复定义 | ❌ 报错 | ✅ 自动合并 |\n",
    "\n",
    "### OpenClaw 中的选择\n",
    "\n",
    "```typescript\n",
    "// 项目中更常用 type（简洁）\n",
    "export type MessagingTarget = {\n",
    "  kind: MessagingTargetKind;\n",
    "  id: string;\n",
    "};\n",
    "\n",
    "// interface 用于需要扩展的场景\n",
    "interface BaseConfig {\n",
    "  port: number;\n",
    "}\n",
    "\n",
    "interface GatewayConfig extends BaseConfig {\n",
    "  host: string;\n",
    "}\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "**建议**：简单对象用 `type`，需要扩展用 `interface`。"
   ]
  },
